data.description: Wonderful split bedroom open floor plan! Large sized living room open to kitchen. A kitchen with island and walk in pantry! Oversized, inviting Master suite offers 2 large walk in closets and private bath with dual vanities, garden tub and separate shower. Scenic community park with pond, open green space, jogging paths and playground. New roof as of this past month.
